 with carbamazepine.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/161523/', '', 'Capreomycin, Pyrazinamide, Rifamycin, Streptomycin, Cycloserine, Rifabutin, Pyridoxine, Ethionamide, Pretomanid, Aminosalicylic acid', 'Phenelzine, Tranylcypromine, Desvenlafaxine, Maprotiline, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, More', 1767369485);
